Jekyll Template for Blogging

SalFollow Author of Mediumish, a Bootstrap Medium styled template available for WordPress, HTML, Ghost and Jekyll. You are currently previewing Jekyll template demo.

여기에 프로젝트 소개 - 자바스크립트 알고리즘

If you already have a full Ruby development environment with all headers and RubyGems installed (see Jekyll’s requirements), you can create a new Jekyll site by doing the following:

# Install Jekyll and Bundler gems through RubyGems
gem install jekyll bundler

# Create a new Jekyll site at ./myblog
jekyll new myblog

# Change into your new directory
cd myblog

# Build the site on the preview server
bundle exec jekyll serve

# Now browse to http://localhost:4000
